data.title: FIFA 19 — All Leagues and Clubs
data.meta_description: Over 700 teams in over 30 leagues are playable at launch in FIFA 19.
data.text:
EA SPORTS™ FIFA 19 for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC is more connected to real-world football than ever, thanks to the addition and enhancement of some of the world's biggest clubs and leagues. From the UEFA Champions League to Italy's Serie A TIM, you'll have more options than ever when picking the right club for you in FIFA 19.

Historic European clubs like Dinamo Zagreb, Slavia Praha, Dynamo Kyiv, and Viktoria Plzeň are now included, forming a list of over 700 playable teams at launch on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC. Full licenses for Serie A TIM and Chinese Super League have also been added, meaning that many of the world's biggest leagues are now available across FIFA 19.

LaLiga Santander has also received a big makeover for FIFA 19 with the addition of many new stadiums and player head scans, in addition to the dazzling and authentic broadcast package.

The UEFA Champions League, UEFA Europa League, and UEFA Super Cup are also fully integrated into FIFA 19, meaning that you can take on the best in Europe and lift the famous trophies across a variety of modes. Get immersed in the world's biggest club competitions with officially licensed details, from match presentation to an all-new commentary crew.

FIFA 19 is available for pre-order* now ahead of a worldwide release on PlayStation®4, Xbox One, and PC on September 28.

* Conditions and restrictions apply. See Game and Offer disclaimers for full details.
